          "content": "在页面上：\n- Repository name 填 `roleplay_game`\n- 选 Public 或 Private\n- **不要**勾选 Add README / .gitignore / license\n- 点 Create repository\n\n**第 2 步**：创建完成后回来告诉我，我执行推送命令：\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/glencai/Documents/kiro/roleplay_game\ngit remote add origin https://github.com/apertus-dev/roleplay_game.git\ngit push -u origin main\n```\n\n仓库创建好了吗？"
        }
